You are here: SALESFORCE HELP DOCS SERVICE CLOUD Customizing a Call Center Directory

Every call center in Salesforce CRM Call Center includes a call center directory that allows users to search for phone numbers throughout your organization.

Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
User permissions needed: Manage Call Centers

You can customize call center directories by:
Adding additional directory numbers
Updating phone number search layouts
title: Customizing Call Center Directories
